 class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好心媾女就咪帶婚戒啦 唔覆你好正常"},{"pid":"c9784438df9ec75584a9f5fa0137c1fc1e479de9","tid":2477890,"uid":125017,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T15:54:06.000Z","msg":"廿分鐘蒸到條魚下話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定要去超市買魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBTW 咁個銷魂飯呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eec793ca2a3ee4d5d40d7c174e14a5f8b61f73c","tid":2477890,"uid":107656,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T15:57:31.000Z","msg":"菜又收錢<br />\n白飯又收錢<br />\n咁你嗌個餐黎把撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5f680db3afd5db774908f2ba3b6c48ecd21194","tid":2477890,"uid":294121,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T15:59:21.000Z","msg":"條女身形柒撚到<br />\n頭大身細腰長過條腿<br />\n後面條仔仲好J<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6fbda0d4b026cf5cc662769dbb848e4693814b6","tid":2477890,"uid":31841,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T16:00:45.000Z","msg":"又嚟搞鳩閪杰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n閪杰已經有精神病喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429195beb67164e70eb560b648bfc3c113dfb837","tid":2477890,"uid":84588,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T16:01:38.000Z","msg":"衰完一穫又一穫<br />\n不如真係執啦<br />\n無心做都好啲<br />\n有心做都搞到咁<br />\n張生又辛苦<br />\n食客又辛苦<br />\n我唔信黃絲全部無個係醒嘅<br />\n點解張生請親嘅無論係廚定落單都係咁嘅水平"},{"pid":"9f390cf9d2dd2dcbcb7dcd0b6cc0d2fcbe6a382c","tid":2477890,"uid":31841,"like":1,"dislike":4