\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160bb80e623495e7b12f6a0123f60f848a5c15f8","tid":2477890,"uid":57844,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T17:20:36.000Z","msg":"拿，之後套路就係咁：<br />\n聽日龍門fb 就出道歉文，老闆會話以後蒸魚必定快，仲送油菜<br />\n聽日下晝連登打手就出龍門食評讚到天上有地下無"},{"pid":"6e6174869de3753c72bbdb04a0f35877c1868247","tid":2477890,"uid":86813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"430d0b106f366b701b2905bacbdceeefe9c9ee53","tid":2477890,"uid":272677,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73bead9a7715aee43af9f883de112d367804280f","tid":2477890,"uid":162513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T15:40:26.000Z","msg":"是咁的～<br />\n<br />\nFB見到瓏門告急，又執達吏又盛，即刻打手mode上身，趁5日長假約左女神一齊食瓏門<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：女神<br />\n<br />\n（正常晚飯時間 7:30pm)<br />\n女神（泱泱樣）：師兄，黎個咖哩焗豬+茶走，大家咁話～<br />\n阿姐：唔好意思賣晒<br />\n女神：err,咁有冇咖哩咩咩？<br />\n阿姐：都賣晒啦<br />\n女神：errrr, 咁要個黯然銷魂飯啦...<br />\n我：我要梅菜蒸鯇魚唔該<br />\n阿姐：鯇魚賣晒喇(88蚊)倉魚啦好嘛(138蚊）<br />\n我：ok冇問題<br />\n<br />\n我安慰個frd， 人地就執笠，餐牌唔齊好正常。<br />\n其實我一直對瓏門/渣哥所有是非都充耳不聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃店就係黃店，食親都係黃店。<br />\n港共借疫情故意打壓餐飲業，已是司馬昭之心，路人皆知，睇死冇app夠膽再post「黃店原因」，執左笠疫情後再開返都冇人信<br />\n<br />\n女神有少少潔癖上身，又嫌人地餐具唔乾淨，搵紙巾係咁抺；又嫌人地廁所有曱甴，我心入面真係嗤之以鼻：而家啲90後真係唔捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到8:30，連我都胃痛到忍唔住，用禮貌態度追左張俊傑老闆：唔好意思，我地7:30嗌嘅魚仲未到，而家真係好肚餓。<br />\n張老闆好識做，即刻送左碟菜同炒蛋畀我地。我仲同女神講：嗱，呢啲咪識做生意囉，抵佢做到龍頭。但我同女神都已經傾左成個鐘，漸漸冇咩話題，有啲尷尬，9:00再禮貌地追左張老闆一次<br />\n<br />\n去到9:20，feel到女神有啲唔耐煩，我再笑住口咁追左靚女waitress一次。條魚終於上，我再追個waiter:「白飯未黎 」點知佢出新單收我白飯錢....我話：白飯係套餐包嫁喎.....（其實我碟菜套餐都包，佢都收多左我錢.....懶得拗喇當小費）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HL2aXCU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHL2aXCU.png&h=44a698ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結果女神望住我食到10:00，相顧無言。<br />\n<br />\n我仲安慰佢話：人地就執笠，體諒下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n埋單時阿姐同我講：多謝晒！下次再黎幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女神：FB唔係話4月1執笠咩！？<br />\n阿姐：冇生意先執嘛，而家有你地支持咪繼續囉，記得多啲黎喇！！<br />\n<br />\n去到呢刻，我就好似見到許腎IG張「清明上河圖」咁無奈，而我已經分不清，呢個係瓏門嘅 復活節 定 愚人節隱藏menu<br />\n<br />\nPS:女神已經冇覆我Signal 3日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點氹返佢好.....在線等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS: 我用極飢餓狀態望住個靚女waitress 120分鐘<br />\n佢可能誤會左我係毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7qcaW5V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7qcaW5V.png&h=e3ebe25e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T15:44:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />圖一隻婚戒係咩事？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />圖二靚女有無 ig"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T17:22:07.000Z","msg":"偷情<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48cdf5bf81ebebbd34bad78406bba97092bf2aa7","tid":2477890,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T17:24:04.000Z","msg":"召喚 UST南亞仔"},{"pid":"09ce0cd15b4489c8520b69c3dbacf9376784f8fd","tid":2477890,"uid":32586,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T17:25:11.000Z","msg":"有冇法國文章開頭個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完全冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35bf9f71c5ae6bce19f5b7c39392e70452299c2","tid":2477890,"uid":116696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T17:25:56.000Z","msg":"又抹黑<br />\n次次都揀凌晨趁人瞓晒先開工"},{"pid":"c26f9b0e3b9c32df499f031049cddcdb613f3126","tid":2477890,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T17:29:22.000Z","msg":"條女瘦到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f9a41df49db520dd2d179f6a8a32620f6dd217","tid":2477890,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T17:29:56.000Z","msg":"今日好多人？ 阿傑真係成日柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 你人真好 唔同佢講收多咗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab55c87b6c27e3e9624b8f929e1e6e2c657bdbd7","tid":2477890,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"48cdf5bf81ebebbd34bad78406bba97092bf2aa7","tid":2477890,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T17:24:04.000Z","msg":"召喚 UST南亞仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T17:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354d256abda64456e737c77cacb9f0c2cf2f16c7","tid":2477890,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08f9a41df49db520dd2d179f6a8a32620f6dd217","tid":2477890,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T17:29:56.000Z","msg":"今日好多人？ 阿傑真係成日柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 你人真好 唔同佢講收多咗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h